{"tid":816701,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"尖嘴彌敦道的士九巴相撞 1死4傷","createTime":"2018-09-13T02:04:44.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-13T05:11:59.000Z","uid":19287,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"d897a7c65ddb1cf9970191370bf4630e63747446","tid":816701,"uid":19287,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-13T02:04:44.000Z","msg":"09:00】老婦送院不治，另外兩車司機及兩名乘客共4人受傷送院<br />\n<br />\n早上8時14分，尖沙嘴彌敦道南行線近麼地道，有九巴與的士相撞。的士繼而鏟上行人路，撞塌欄杆和路牌。兩車司機及巴士上3名乘客受傷，其中一名女乘客昏迷，由救護車送院，其後證實不治。的士有載客，乘客無恙。警方現正在場調查，彌敦道一段慢線及麼地道暫時封閉。<br />\n<br />\n讀者盧太途經金域假日酒店門口，見到一輛87D線九巴與的士相撞，的士鏟上行人路撞塌路牌。她表示，當時有一名傷者已經上救護車，另有一名女傷者倒卧巴士的落車門位置，救援人員正在場協助。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/13/100439_e699f55013d57c64725318656e02ad16.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F13%2F100439_e699f55013d57c64725318656e02ad16.png&h=7b9919f5&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/13/100440_e699f55013d57c64725318656e02ad16.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F13%2F100440_e699f55013d57c64725318656e02ad16.png&h=6fb88750&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/13/100441_e68e3e3b4bf4e51a75c6eb854f551e2b.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F13%2F100441_e68e3e3b4bf4e51a75c6eb854f551e2b.png&h=380e620b&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"de141f3cea627f09d2de9f399f66afaa7f3554c7","tid":816701,"uid":19287,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-13T02:06:02.000Z","msg":"阿婆比的士佬搞到仆一仆就rip<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1b208aa092dbe08542ac14cd8430297d06fb669f","tid":816701,"uid":23707,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-13T02:15:35.000Z","msg":"DC9亂CUT??"},{"pid":"7dc24a8c1d76d9fe891ee68a560384cd758932ee","tid":816701,